snippet.title: Celeste Strawberry Jam | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
The Celeste Strawberry Jam Collaboration is a mod that has been in development for 2 years. It features 5 difficulty levels for new and experienced players alike, with over a hundred unique levels to play. We hope you all enjoy!

Watch our installation guide: https://youtu.be/h-f2unIoafA

Play here: https://gamebanana.com/mods/424541
Report issues in our Discord Server: https://discord.gg/8zx245Ha3x

Bandcamp and streaming revenue from the original soundtrack will go to benefit Trans Lifeline. You can read more about Trans Lifeline: https://translifeline.org/
Find our Bandcamp page here: https://celestestrawberryjam.bandcamp.com/

Play Celeste: http://www.celestegame.com/
Download the Everest API Mod Loader: https://everestapi.github.io/
Download mods on the Celeste Gamebanana page: https://gamebanana.com/games/6460

Join the Celeste Community on Discord: https://discord.gg/celeste

Trailer Edited by fonda1515
Trailer Music by BeanJammin, Ceph, catapillie, and Aidan (quadratic97)
Thumbnail by nerferd_
